      "title": "A letter from Gotabaya to Putin",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa has sent a letter to Russian President Vladimir Putin requesting his cooperation in purchasing oil.",
        "The two presidents are expected to make a phone call these days and a Sri Lankan delegation is expected to leave for Moscow. Sri Lanka is currently facing a severe fuel shortage."
      ],
